					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The 4bpp EGA modes are planar frame buffers, but CGA graphics is a 2bpp packed frame buffer. Virtual Boy and Neo Geo Pocket use 2bpp packed tiles. The 4bpp low-color mode of Macintosh Color QuickDraw is a packed frame buffer.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

